%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20air%20quality%20drops%20to%20'very%20poor'%20category%2C%20Grap-IV%20measures%20lifted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735099639000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-quality-drops-to-very-poor-category-grap-iv-measures-lifted-124122500116_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20stringent%20measures%20under%20the%20stage-IV%20of%20the%20Grap%20in%20Delhi%20were%20lifted%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20following%20an%20improvement%20in%20the%20AQI%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2240%20Hours%20On%2C%203-Year-Old%20Girl%20Still%20Stuck%20Inside%20700-Feet%20Rajasthan%20Borewell%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%2040%20hours%20on%2C%20rescue%20efforts%20are%20still%20underway%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20to%20save%20a%20three-year-old%20girl%20who%20fell%20into%20a%20700-foot%20borewell%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Kotputli-Behror%20district.%20The%20girl%2C%20Chetna%2C%20fell%20into%20the%20borewell%20while%20she%20was%20playing%20on%20her%20father's%20farm%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teams%20of%20the%20State%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(SDRF)%2C%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%2C%20and%20other%20officials%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20rescue%20operations.%20However%2C%20they%20have%20been%20facing%20difficulties%20due%20to%20the%20narrow%20width%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchetna-girl-3-stuck-in-700-foot-borewell-in-rajasthan-for-20-hours-rescue-ops-on-7321230%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eborewell%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20soil%20around%20her%20was%20compacted%20due%20to%20moisture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20were%20initially%20trying%20to%20rescue%20her%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20hook%20attached%20to%2010-foot%20iron%20rods.%20While%20that