20tourism%20is%20an%20important%20means%20of%20livelihood%2C%20there%20are%20a%20sizable%20number%20of%20homestays%20and%20lodges.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20best%20to%20make%20bookings%20in%20advance%2C%20particularly%20during%20the%20holiday%20season%2C%20Sasang%20recommends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDoes%20it%20snow%20in%20Sandakphu%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes!%20The%20higher%20altitudes%20have%20traditionally%20been%20blessed%20with%20snowfall%20between%20the%20months%20of%20December%20and%20February.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20become%20a%20tad%20bit%20erratic%2C%20thanks%20to%20climate%20change.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20some%20light%20snowfall%20in%20September%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sasang.%20%E2%80%9CLast%20year%2C%20it%20snowed%20in%20March.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20inform%20me%20that%20the%20best%20time%20to%20make%20the%20trek%20is%20between%20September%20and%20November%20when%20the%20skies%20are%20crystal%20clear%2C%20or%20March%20and%20April%20when%20the%20forests%20are%20lush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20up%20for%20it%2C%20any%20time%20is%20a%20good%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-24-at-15.40.39_11zon-1735043669.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20singular%20lodge%20covered%20in%20snow%20in%20Phalut%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-24-at-15.40.39_11zon-1735043669.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-24-at-15.40.39_11zon-1735043669-300x138.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-24-at-15.40.39_11zon-1735043669-500x230.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2