%20and%202019-20%20financial%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulator%20has%20fined%20CA%20AB%20Jani%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20and%20barred%20him%20for%20five%20years%20from%20being%20appointed%20as%20an%20auditor%20or%20internal%20auditor%20or%20from%20undertaking%20any%20audit%20in%20respect%20of%20financial%20statements%20or%20internal%20audit%20of%20the%20functions%20and%20activities%20of%20any%20company.%20A%20fine%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20has%20been%20imposed%20on%20CA%20Rakesh%20Sharma%20and%20the%20regulator%20has%20banned%20him%20for%20three%20years%20from%20being%20appointed%20as%20an%20auditor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mr%20Jani%20was%20the%20Engagement%20Partner%20(EP)%2C%20Mr%20Sharma%20was%20the%20Engagement%20Quality%20Control%20Review%20(EQCR)%20Partner%20for%20the%20audit%20of%20the%20company%20for%202018-19%20and%202019-%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20has%20NFRA%20fined%20Deloitte%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulator's%20action%20stems%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinancial-watchdog-nfra-fines-deloitte-rs-2-crore-over-zee-audit-7324836%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeloitte%3C%2Fa%3E's%20alleged%20failure%20to%20identify%20and%20report%20irregularities%20related%20to%20a%20Rs%20200%20crore%20fixed%20deposit%20held%20by%20ZEEL%20in%20Yes%20Bank.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20ZEEL%20Chairman%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20promoter%20of%20the%20Essel%20Group%2C%20issued%20a%20letter%20to%20Yes%20Bank%2C%20committing%20Rs%20200%20crore%20fixed%20deposit%20of%20ZEEL%20as%20a%20guarantee%20for%20the%20loans%20given%20by%20Yes%20Bank%20to%20a%20promoter%20group%20company%20Essel%20Green%20Mobility%20Ltd.%20The%20bank%20appropriated%20the%20fixed%20deposit%20in%20July%202019%20towards%20the%20settlement%20of%20loan%20amounts%20due%20from%20seven%20promoter%20group%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NFRA%2C%20its%20examination%20showed%20that%20the%