ing%20him%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%20Kambli%20(52)%20is%20responding%20to%20the%20treatment%20for%20urinary%20tract%20infections%20for%20which%20he%20was%20admitted%20at%20Akruti%20Hospital%20near%20Bhiwandi%20town%20on%20Saturday%20(December%2021)%2C%20Dr%20Vivek%20Trivedi%20told%20PTI.%20Trivedi%20is%20heading%20the%20medical%20team%20that%20is%20supervising%20the%20former%20cricketer's%20health.%20Doctors%20were%20planning%20to%20do%20an%20MRI%20(magnetic%20resonance%20imaging)%20on%20the%20former%20India%20batter%2C%20but%20since%20he%20has%20developed%20a%20fever%2C%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20non-invasive%20medical%20procedure%20will%20be%20taken%20later%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20MRI%20procedure%20has%20been%20necessitated%20after%20a%20series%20of%20medical%20examinations%20conducted%20earlier%20revealed%20clots%20in%20his%20brain%2C%20Trivedi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKambli%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20shifted%20out%20of%20the%20ICU%20within%20a%20day%20or%20two%20and%20discharged%20after%20about%20four%20days%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20Mumbai-based%20former%20cricketer%20was%20critical%20four%20days%20back%20when%20he%20had%20an%20extreme%20urinary%20infection%20as%20puss%20had%20got%20collected%20in%20his%20bladder.%20The%20puss%20was%20removed%20when%20he%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemaining%20at%20home%20for%20some%20more%20days%20would%20have%20complicated%20his%20condition%2C%20Trivedi%20opined%2C%20adding%20his%20blood%20pressure%20was%20also%20fluctuating%20when%20he%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20condition%20was%20stable%20at%20present%2C%20the%20doctor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20condition%20will%20be%20closely%20monitored%20for%20the%20next%2024%20hours%20and%20a%20decision%20taken%20on%20shifting%20him%20out%20of%20the%20ICU%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Mi