rts.%20The%20country%20knows%20that%20Manu%20has%20done%20such%20a%20great%20feat%20that%20the%20whole%20country%20was%20proud%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManu%20Bhaker%20opened%20India's%20medal%20tally%20in%20the%20Olympics%20after%20she%20secured%20third%20place%20in%20the%20women's%20individual%2010m%20air%20pistol%20event%2C%20becoming%20the%20first-ever%20woman%20shooter%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20medal%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20made%20history%20for%20India%20in%20the%20Paris%202024%20Olympics%20by%20securing%20two%20bronze%20medals%20in%20the%20shooting%20event.%20Manu%20with%20Sarabjot%20Singh%20secured%20bronze%20in%20the%2010M%20Air%20Pistol%20Mixed%20team%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20of%20Manu%20and%20Sarabjot%20defeated%20South%20Korea's%20Lee%20Wonho%20and%20Oh%20Ye%20Jin%2016-10%20in%20the%20bronze%20medal%20play-off%20match.%20Both%20Manu%20and%20Sarabjot%20shot%20consistently%20with%20regular%2010s%20in%20the%20series%20against%20the%20South%20Koreans%20to%20claim%20India's%20second%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarabjot%20and%20Manu%20secured%20the%20bronze%20medal%20in%20the%2010m%20air%20pistol%20(mixed%20team)%20event%2C%20which%20was%20India's%20first-ever%20shooting%20team%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20final%20event%2C%20she%20narrowly%20missed%20out%20on%20the%20historic%20grand%20treble%20and%20finished%20fourth%20in%20the%20women's%2025m%20pistol%20shooting%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735093020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fdl59pkso_manu-bhaker-afp_625x300_25_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fshooting%2Fsports-ministry-reacts-to-khel-ratna-row-involving-manu-bhaker-no-list-7325116%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manu%20Bhaker%20's%20name%20has%20not%20been%20excluded%20from%20the%20Major%20Dhyan%20Chand%20Khel%20Ratna%20Award%20list%20and%20the%20final%20names%20for%20the%20National%20Sports%20Awards%20have