dly%20cancelled%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Ftourists-get-disappointed-after-midnight-christmas-prayers-at-shimlas-christ-church-gets-cancell-7326333%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex%20Government%20Employee-Turned-Tycoon%20Under%20Lens%20In%20Big%20Bhopal%20Gold%20Seizure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20constable-turned-builder%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20being%20investigated%20by%20multiple%20central%20agencies%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20corruption%20case.%20The%20case%20is%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%2C%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20and%20Lokayukta%20with%20each%20agency%20focusing%20on%20different%20aspects%20of%20the%20case%2C%20which%20came%20to%20light%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2019%2C%20assets%20worth%20Rs%207.98%20crore%2C%20including%20Rs%202.87%20crore%20in%20cash%20and%20234%20kilograms%20of%20silver%20were%20seized%20after%20searches%20at%20the%20properties%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassets-worth-rs-8-crore-seized-from-ex-constable-in-madhya-pradesh-7319032%5C%22%3ESaurabh%20Sharma%20%3C%2Fa%3E-%20a%20former%20constable%20in%20the%20state%20transport%20department%20-%20in%20Bhopal%20by%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Lokayukta's%20Special%20Police%20Establishment%20(SPE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20gained%20momentum%20when%2052%20kg%20gold%20and%20Rs%2011%20crore%20cash%20were%20found%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbhopal-news%2Fgold-worth-rs-40-crore-cash-found-in-abandoned-innova-in-bhopal-jungle-7292848%5C%22%3Eabandoned%20SUV%3C%2Fa%3E%20parked%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Bhopal%20the%20same%20day.%20The%20car%20was%20found%20in%20the%20Mendori%20forest%20on%20the%20city's%20outskirts%20following%20inputs%20that%20gold%20was%20being%20transported%20via%20jungle%20route.%20Several%20witnesses%20reported%20seeing%20armed%20individuals%20abandoning%20the%20vehicle.%20Acting%20on%20a%20tip-off%2C%20IT%20officials%20seized%20the%20car%20under%20section%20132%20of%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Act%2C%20treating%20it%20as%20an%20independent%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Innova%20car%20reportedly%20belongs%20to%20Chetan%20Gaur%2C%20an%20associate%20of%20Saurabh%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20has%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20against%20Mr%20Sharma%20and%20Mr%20Gaur.%20Mr%20Sharma%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20fled%20to%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20is%20working%20to%20trace%20the%20origins%20of%20the%20unaccounted%20gold%2C%20adding%20another%20layer%20to%20the%20investigation.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Lokayukta's%20SPE%20has%20also%20intensified%20its%20probe%20and%20summons%20have%20been%20issued%20to%20Mr%20Sharma%2C%20his%20family%20members%2C%20and%20close%20associates%2C%20including%20Mr%20Gaur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma's%20journey%20from%20a%20transport%20department%20constable%20to%20a%20real%20estate%20magnate%20is%20also%20under%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20father%20RK%20Sharma%20was%20a%20government%20doctor%20and%20died%20in%202015.%20Afterwards%2C%20Saurabh%20Sharma%20was%20appointed%20as%20a%20constable%20in%20the%20state%20transport%20department%20on%20compassionate%20grounds%20in%202015%20and%20took%20voluntary%20retirement%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20taking%20voluntary%20retirement%20in%202023%2C%20he%20entered%20the%20real%20estate%20sector%2C%20forming%20ties%20with%20prominent%20builders%20in%20Bhopal.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20constable%20used%20money%20earned%20through%20corrupt%20means%20to%20amass%20huge%20assets%2C%20including%20setting%20up%20a%20school%20and%20hotel%20in%20the%20name%20of%20his%20mother%2C%20wife%2C%20sister-in-law%20and%20close%20associates%20Gaur%20and%20Sharad%20Jaiswal%2C%20a%20Lokayukta%20SPE%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20sources%2C%20documents%20from%20several%20income%20tax%20raids%20unearthed%20Rs%20100%20crore%20in%20alleged%20transactions%20involving%20transport%20department%20officials%20across%2052%20districts%2C%20suggesting%20a%20sprawling%20network%20of%20corruption.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20also%20points%20to%20systemic%20corruption%20within%20the%20transport%20department%2C%20with%20allegations%20against%20senior%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20also%20sparked%20a%20political%20row.%20Former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Digvijay%20Singh%20has%20called%20for%20a%20judicial%20probe%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court's%20Chief%20Justice.%20In%20a%20letter%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20criticised%20the%20handling%20of%20the%20case%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20ED%20and%20IT%20departments%20take%20exclusive%20control%20of%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Yadav%2C%20responding%20to%20the%20allegations%2C%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20government%20has%20always%20fought%20a%20principled%20battle%20against%20corruption.%20We%20had%20even%20shut%20down%20check%20barriers.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20combating%20corruption%20at%20every%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735092420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fgts6q1p_madhya-pradesh-seizure_625x300_25_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fex-government-employee-turned-tycoon-saurabh-sharma-under-lens-in-big-bhopal-gold-seizure-7325041%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20constable-turned-builder%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20being%20investiga