count%20expected%20to%20rise.%20The%20attacks%2C%20which%20took%20place%20on%20the%20night%20of%20December%2024%2C%20reportedly%20targeted%20seven%20villages%2C%20including%20Laman%2C%20where%20five%20members%20of%20a%20family%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20sources%20claim%20that%20Pakistani%20jets%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20bombings.%20Reports%20indicate%20that%20the%20Murg%20Bazaar%20village%20in%20Barmal%20was%20destroyed%2C%20exacerbating%20the%20ongoing%20humanitarian%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airstrikes%20have%20caused%20severe%20civilian%20casualties%20and%20widespread%20destruction%2C%20further%20escalating%20tensions%20in%20the%20region.%20As%20recovery%20efforts%20continue%2C%20further%20investigation%20is%20required%20to%20confirm%20details%20and%20clarify%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attacks%2C%20reported%20Khaama%20Press.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Taliban's%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20has%20vowed%20to%20retaliate%20following%20the%20airstrike%20on%20Barmal%2C%20Paktika.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20stated%20that%20defending%20their%20land%20and%20sovereignty%20is%20their%20legitimate%20right%2C%20and%20condemned%20the%20attack%2C%20claiming%20that%20%26quot%3BWaziristani%20refugees%26quot%3B%20were%20among%20those%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pakistani%20officials%20have%20not%20officially%20confirmed%20the%20airstrike%2C%20security%20sources%20close%20to%20the%20military%20suggested%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20aimed%20at%20Taliban%20hideouts%20near%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20amid%20escalating%20tensions%20between%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20the%20presence%20of%20Pakistani%20militants%20in%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistani%20Taliban%2C%20or%20Tehreek-e-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP)%2C%20has%20increased%20its%20attacks%20on%20Pakistani%20forces%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20with%20Pakistan%20accusing%20the%20Afghan%20Taliban%20of%