edy%20justice%20for%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%208%20pm%2C%20they%20lit%20candles%20near%20their%20make-shift%20stage%20as%20part%20of%20their%20'Droher%20Alo%20Jalan'%20initiative.%20The%20protesters%20were%20also%20joined%20by%20a%20good%20number%20of%20people%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20like%20to%20extend%20our%20protest%20demonstration%20till%20December%2031.%20We%20shall%20again%20move%20the%20court%20seeking%20permission%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20agitating%20senior%20doctors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agitators%20also%20formed%20a%20human%20chain%20at%20the%20Dorina%20Crossing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20on%20Monday%20upheld%20a%20December%2020%20order%20allowing%20doctors%20to%20hold%20demonstrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20had%20challenged%20the%20single%20bench%20order%20by%20Justice%20Tirthankar%20Ghosh%2C%20which%20permitted%20the%20Joint%20Forum%20of%20Doctors%20to%20stage%20a%20sit-in%20%26quot%3B50%20feet%20away%20from%20Dorina%20Crossing%20at%20Esplanade%20in%20central%20Kolkata%20from%20December%2020-26.%26quot%3B%20Police%20had%20discovered%20the%20body%20of%20the%20woman%20doctor%20inside%20the%20RG%20Kar%20hospital%20on%20August%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20since%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20the%20prime%20accused%2C%20Sanjay%20Roy%2C%20for%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20the%20on-duty%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20Roy%2C%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20with%20the%20local%20police%2C%20allegedly%20committed%20the%20crime%20when%20the%20victim%20was%20resting%20in%20the%20hospital's%20seminar%20room%20during%20a%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735090020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ffsvedvc_rg-kar-protest_625x300_09_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-probe-doctors-stage-protest-over-cbi-delay-in-kolkata-rape-murder-probe-7326084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20part%20of%20their%20protest%2C%20the%20junior%20doctors%20symbolically%20locked%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20CBI%20office%20at%20the%20CGO%20Complex%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20agency%20expedite%20the%20probe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-probe-doctors-stage-protest-over-cbi-delay-in-kolkata-rape-murder-probe-7326084%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Engaged%20At%202%2C%20Married%20At%2016%3A%20Childhoods%20'Chained'%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Village%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20heart%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20nestled%20amid%20the%20rugged%20terrains%20of%20Rajgarh%20district%2C%20lies%20Jaitpura%20-%20a%20village%20where%20time%20seems%20to%20have%20stopped%2C%20leaving%20dreams%20in%20shackles%20and%20childhoods%20stolen.%20Here%2C%20innocence%20is%20traded%2C%20and%20the%20cruel%20weight%20of%20tradition%20drags%20children%20into%20adulthood%20long%20before%20their%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20journey%20began%20where%20the%20road%20ended%2C%20over%20narrow%2C%20broken%20paths%20that%20echoed%20the%20hardship%20of%20lives%20untouched%20by%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20forgotten%20corners%20of%20India%2C%20we%20found%20children%20whose%20laughter%20has%20been%20silenced%20by%20customs%20like%20child%20marriage%20and%20engagement%2C%20bound%20by%20the%20age-old%20practice%20of%20Jhagda-Natra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20grim%20tradition%20demands%20exorbitant%20amounts%20from%20families%20seeking%20to%20break%20free%20from%20pre-arranged%20marriages%2C%20perpetuating%20a%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20and%20despair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stories%20of%20Jaitpura%20are%20a%20reflection%20of%20a%20broader%20malaise%20plaguing%2050%20villages%2C%20where%20over%20700%20children%20have%20lost%20their%20right%20to%20a%20carefree%20childhood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERama%20Bai%2C%20now%2040%2C%20recalls%20how%20her%20childhood%20ended%20abruptly%20three%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20married%20at%20the%20age%20of%2010%20years...%20Every%20day%2C%20girls%20here%20are%20married%20off.%20This%20must%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20her%20voice%20heavy%20with%20the%20weight%20of%20her%20past.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeeta%2C%20just%2022%2C%20carries%20her%20young%20daughter%20in%20her%20arms.%20Engaged%20at%20two%2C%20married%20at%2016%2C%20she%20refuses%20to%20let%20history%20repeat%20itself.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20engage%20my%20daughter.%20This%20must%20end%20with%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserts%2C%20her%20resolve%20a%20tiny%20ray%20of%20light%20amid%20the%20darkness%20that%20lies%20heavy%20over%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20parent%20explained%20the%20harsh%20reality%3A%20%26quot%3BHere%20relationships%20are%20often%20fixed%20even%20before%20birth.%20When%20a%20woman%20is%20six%20months%20pregnant%2C%20families%20decide-'if%20you%20have%20a%20boy%20and%20we%20have%20a%20girl%2C%20they%20will%20be%20engaged.'%20They%20stick%20to%20their%20word.%20As%20children%20grow%2C%20more%20money%20is%20required%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20in%20a%20drunken%20state%2C%20engagements%20are%20finalised.%20This%20happened%20in%20our%20family%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20a%20tone%20of%20resignation%20in%20her%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChildhood%20Dreams%20in%20Chains%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20decisions%20impact%20children%20profoundly%2C%20robbing%20them%20of%20their%20innocence%20and%20dreams.%20Some%20are%20as%20young%20as%20one%20year%20old%20when%20they%20are%20engaged%2C%20marked%20with%20bracelets%20or%20lockets%20to%20signify%20the%20commitment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDinesh%2C%20a%20young%20boy%2C%20shared%20a%20bittersweet%20moment%20about%20his%20fiancee%3A%20%26quot%3BMy%20fiancee%20is%20frim%20Gangapar.%20She%20was%20given%20a%20bracelet%20and%20a%20pendent%20during%20the%20engagement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20child%2C%20Mangilal's%20fianc%26amp%3B%23233%3Be%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20a%20year%20old%20when%20I%20got%20engaged.%20I%20don't%20remember%20much%2C%20but%20I%20know%20his%20name%20is%20Mangilal.%20I%20didn't%20receive%20anything%20during%20the%20engagement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%2C%20these%20symbols%20of%20commitment%20are%20not%20cherished%20but%20burdensome.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20boy%2C%20just%2010%20years%20old%2C%20was%20vocal%20about%20his%20discomfort.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20given%20sweets%20when%20I%20got%20engaged%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to.%20I've%20decided-I%20won't%20marry.%20I'm%20in%20the%205th%20standard%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20become%20a%20doctor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20young%20girls%2C%20anklets%20and%20bangles%20are%20not%20adornments%20but%20symbols%20of%20oppression.%20The%20pain%2C%20both%20physical%20and%20emotional%2C%20weighs%20heavily%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20feet%20hurt%20a%20lot%20because%20of%20the%20anklets.%20I%20tell%20my%20parents%20every%20day%2C%20but%20they%20say%20I%20must%20wear%20them.%20This%20is%20bondage.%20I%20want%20freedom%20from%20these%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20girl%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20most%2C%20these%20ornaments%20represent%20a%20lifelong%20burden.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2010-year-old%2C%20married%20when%20she%20was%20far%20younger%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20bangles%20were%20put%20on%20me%20during%20my%20engagement%20and%20marriage.%20They're%20said%20to%20enhance%20a%20girl's%20beauty%2C%20but%20to%20me%2C%20they%20are%20shackles.%20Sometimes%2C%20when%20there%20is%20trouble%20at%20my%20in-laws'%20house%2C%20these%20bangles%20are%20removed%20and%20sold.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVillagers%20justify%20the%20system%20as%20a%20compulsion%20-%20a%20way%20to%20escape%20debt%2C%20or%20wedding%20expenses.%20But%20it%20is%20the%20children%20who%20pay%20the%20price%2C%20their%20lives%20reduced%20to%20mere%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovardhan%20Tanwar%2C%20the%20deputy%20sarpanch%2C%20sounded%20matter%20of%20fact.%20%26quot%3BEngagements%20happen%20when%20parents%20are%20drunk.%20They%20take%20loans%2C%20marry%20off%20their%20daughters%2C%20and%20the%20cycle%20continues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey-5%2C%2046%20per%20cent%20of%20women%20aged%2020-24%20in%20Rajgarh%20were%20married%20before%20they%20turned%2018.%20Education%20remains%20a%20distant%20dream%2C%20with%20over%20half%20the%20women%20in%20the%20district%20illiterate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20these%20shackles%20comes%20at%20a%20cost.%20Families%20must%20pay%20hefty%20fines%20to%20annul%20pre-arranged%20marriages%2C%20often%20appearing%20before%20social%20panchayats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%20freedom%20is%20crushing%2C%20leaving%20many%20resigned%20to%20their%20fates.%20In%20certain%20regions%20of%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20if%20a%20girl%20dares%20to%20break%20free%20from%20this%20bondage%20or%20refuses%20to%20go%20through%20with%20a%20prearranged%20marriage%2C%20she%20and%20her%20family%20are%20summoned%20before%20social%20councils.%20These%20councils%20impose%20fines%2C%20known%20as%20'jhagda'%20(penalty)%2C%20for%20canceling%20the%20marriage.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20practices%20like%20nata%20or%20natara%2C%20involving%20widows%20or%20abandoned%20women%20returning%20to%20society%2C%20are%20also%20intertwined%20with%20these%20traditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20these%20statistics%20and%20age-old%20customs%2C%20this%20story%20is%20not%20just%20about%20Jaitpura%20village-it%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20countless%20tales%20of%20pain%20and%20struggle.%20It%20is%20the%20story%20of%20countless%20villages%20where%20tradition%20chains%20childhood%2C%20and%20dreams%20are%20sold.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735089780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F72arrk1o_child-brides-of-mp_625x300_24_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchildhoods-chained-dreams-sold-in-forgotten-corner-of-madhya-pradesh-7324938%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20heart%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20nestled%20amid%20the%20rugged%20terrains%20of%20Rajgarh%20district%2C%20lies%20Jaitpura%20-%20a%20village%20where%20time%20seems%20to%20have%20stopped%2C%20leaving%20dreams%20in%20shackles%20and%20childhoods%20stolen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchildhoods-chained-dreams-sold-in-forgotten-corner-of-madhya-pradesh-7324938%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Santa%20Claus'%20Reindeer-Powered%20Global%20Flight%20To%20Deliver%20Presents%20Underway%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESanta%20Claus%20took%20off%20early%20Christmas%20Eve%20aboard%20his%20reindeer-powered%20sleigh%20to%20deliver%20presents%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20according%20to%20the%20North%20American%20Aerospace%20Defense%20Command%20(NORAD)%2C%20a%20joint%20US%20and%20Canadian%20military%20command%20at%20Peterson%20Space%20Force%20Base%20in%20Colorado%20Springs%20that%20has%20provided%20a%20whimsical%20report%20tracking%20Father%20Christmas%20for%2069%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETracking%20would%20have%20gone%20ahead%20even%20if%20the%20federal%20government%20had%20shut%20down%2C%20a%20crisis%20the%20US%20Congress%20averted%20at%20the%20last%20moment%20this%20past%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSanta%20runs%20on%20the%20Christmas