0the%20active%20ingredient%20in%20Zepbound%20and%20Mounjaro%2C%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20short%20supply%2C%20the%20FDA%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECheaper%20versions%20of%20the%20drug%2C%20known%20as%20compounded%20tirzepatide%2C%20might%20be%20restricted%20in%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPatients%20could%20face%20higher%20costs%20and%20tougher%20access%2C%20and%20telehealth%20is%20racing%20to%20adapt.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FDA%20has%20announced%20that%20popular%20weight%20loss%20medication%20tirzepatide%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20shortage%2C%20potentially%20removing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-how-patients-afford-glp-1-weight-loss-drugs-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeaper%20versions%20of%20the%20drug%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20the%20market%20by%20early%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftirzepatide-weight-loss-drug-vs-semaglutide-glp-1-agonist-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETirzepatide%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20active%20ingredient%20in%20Eli%20Lilly's%20drugs%20Mounjaro%20and%20Zepbound%2C%20branded%20to%20treat%20diabetes%20and%20obesity%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20part%20of%20a%20class%20of%20medications%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGLP-1%20agonists%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20semaglutide%20(sold%20as%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy)%2C%20which%20have%20transformed%20obesity%20treatment%20in%20recent%20years.%20These%20injections%20work%20by%20mimicking%20hormones%20in%20the%20body%20that%20regulate%20appetite%20and%20blood%20sugar%2C%20helping%20patients%20lose%20as%20much%20as%2025%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManufacturers%20have%20struggled%20to%20meet%20the%20intense%20demand%20for%20these%20drugs.%20This%20opened%20the%20door%20for%20pharmacies%20to%20offer%20custom