20per%20year%20and%20an%20incomprehensible%20fallout%20on%20the%20accuracy%20of%20its%20results%20on%20features%20like%20Siri%20and%20Spotlight%2C%20whose%20framework%20is%20largely%20dependent%20on%20Google%20search.%20For%20Google%2C%20besides%20money%20and%20market%20share%2C%20it%20may%20result%20in%20the%20massive%20loss%20of%20its%20entire%20web%20browser%20-%20Chrome.%20It%20also%20faces%20another%20potential%20gigantic%20loss%20-%20its%20Android%20operating%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20finding%20Google%20in%20a%20major%20spot%20of%20bother%2C%20Apple%20has%20sought%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20anti-trust%20trial%20against%20Google%20over%20its%20internet%20search%20engine.%20Apple%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20it%20needs%20to%20step%20in%20as%20it%20cannot%20rely%20on%20Google%20alone%20to%20defend%20the%20revenue-sharing%20agreements%20that%20the%20two%20firms%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20epicenter%20of%20the%20case%2C%20which%20has%20sent%20tremors%20across%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20lies%20in%20an%20agreement%20between%20Google%20and%20Apple%2C%20wherein%20the%20iPhone%2C%20iPad%2C%20and%20Macbook%20maker%20gets%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20each%20year%20for%20making%20Google%20the%20default%20search%20engine%20on%20its%20browser%20-%20Safari.%20In%202022%20alone%2C%20Apple%20reportedly%20received%20in%20excess%20of%20%2420%20billion%20as%20a%20result%20of%20this%20very%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20case%20is%20simple%20-%20Has%20Google%20monopolised%20online%20search%3F%20According%20to%20Google%20-%20No%2C%20it%20has%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20monopoly%20in%20simple%20business%20terms%20is%20a%20situation%20where%20a%20single%20company%20controls%20the%20entire%20market.%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%20it%20becomes%20difficult%20or%20sometimes%20impossible%20for%20the%20competition%20to%20compete%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20level-playing%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFocusing%20on%20this%20very%20point%2C%20Apple's%20lawyers%20submitted%20their%20papers%20to%20the%20court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20in%20which%20they%20conveyed%20that%20Apple%20and%20Google%20are%20not%20competitors%2C%20and%20neither%20does%20Apple%20want%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20search%20engine%20space.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20that%20is%20how%20it%20will%20be%20whether%20or%20not%20Apple%20receives%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars%20from%20Google%20in%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%2C%20in%20its%20petition%2C%20also%20said%20it%20wants%20to%20call%20witnesses%20who%20will%20testify%20under%20oath%20at%20the%20trial%20scheduled%20for%20April%202025.%20On%20that%20day%2C%20the%20prosecutors%20will%20aim%20to%20highlight%20that%20Google%20absolutely%20must%20take%20multiple%20measures%20-%20two%20of%20them%20being%20selling%20its%20Chrome%20browser%20and%20possibly%20its%20Android%20operating%20system%20too.%20The%20prosecutors%20believe%20that%20only%20then%20will%20competition%20be%20restored%20in%20online%20search.%20But%20should%20this%20happen%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20fatal%20blow%20to%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Google's%20parent%20firm%20Alphabet%20is%20figuring%20a%20way%20to%20battle%20this%20grave%20threat%20to%20its%20existence%2C%20Apple%2C%20which%20understand%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation%20has%20said%20%26quot%3BGoogle%20can%20no%20longer%20adequately%20represent%20Apple's%20interests.%20Google%20must%20now%20defend%20against%20a%20broad%20effort%20to%20break%20up%20its%20business%20units.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20justifying%20its%20stand%2C%20Google%20has%20asserted%20that%20the%20entire%20premise%20of%20the%20case%20is%20based%20on%20exclusive%20deals%20-%20and%20that%20is%20what%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20case%20should%20be%20on%2C%20instead%20of%20an%20aim%20to%20breaking%20Google.%20It%20has%20even%20offered%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20such%20deals%20in%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20ending%20the%20deal%20with%20Apple%2C%20Google%20has%20even%20suggested%20that%20it%20is%20willing%20to%20no%20longer%20enter%20any%20agreement%20with%20Android%20phone%20manufacturers%20which%20require%20the%20phone-maker%20to%20set%20Google%20as%20the%20default%20search%20engine%20in%20return%20for%20its%20operating%20system%20and%20supporting%20apps.%20Google%20also%20said%20that%20browser%20companies%20like%20Mozilla%20would%20be%20given%20more%20flexibility%20in%20setting%20rival%20search%20engines%20as%20its%20default%20search.%20This%2C%20according%20to%20Google's%20lawyers%2C%20is%20a%20fair%20solution%20to%20make%20the%20market%20more%20competitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20now%20and%20the%20crucial%20hearing%20in%20April%2C%20Google%20is%20doing%20all%20it%20can%20to%20defend%20itself%20and%20limit%20its%20losses%2C%20should%20it%20lose%20the%20groundbreaking%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20vs%20Google%20is%20poised%20to%20be%20a%20defining%20moment%20for%20the%20global%20tech%20industry%20-%20a%20landmark%20case%20that%20may%20just%20reshape%20how%20the%20world%20uses%20the%20internet.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735070040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fhoacl0c8_google-apple-court_625x300_24_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-google-faces-a-grave-and-uncertain-future-apple-steps-in-heres-why-7324986%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20tech%20behemoths%20-%20Apple%20and%20Google%20-%20are%20coming%20together%20in%20what%20is%20increasingly%20seeming%20like%20an%20indefensible%20case.%20Billions%20and%20billions%20are%20at%20stake%20and%20Google%2C%20the%20world's%20'default'%20search%20engine%2C%20stares%20into%20the%20abyss.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-google-faces-a-grave-and-uncertain-future-apple-steps-i