20were%20a%20major%20advantage%20in%20this%20situation.%20When%20I%20got%20off%20a%20lift%20on%20skis%2C%20I%20felt%20sturdy%20and%20confident.%20I%20never%20fell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20off%20a%20lift%20on%20a%20snowboard%2C%20however%2C%20seemed%20like%20a%20skill%20within%20itself.%20I%20had%20to%20keep%20my%20balance%20while%20pushing%20off%20the%20lift.%20The%20result%20was%20fall%20after%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20first%20day%20of%20snowboarding%2C%20I%20didn't%20successfully%20get%20off%20one%20single%20lift%20without%20falling.%20Meanwhile%2C%20I%20navigated%20lifts%20easily%20on%20my%20first%20day%20of%20skiing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDifferent%20parts%20of%20my%20body%20ached%20after%20both%20skiing%20and%20snowboarding.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20rests%20and%20straps%20into%20her%20snowboard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e5687727e5db0018eefeef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20rests%20and%20straps%20into%20her%20snowboard.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20trying%20skiing%20and%20snowboarding%2C%20I%20didn't%20realize%20how%20hard%20the%20sports%20would%20be%20on%20my%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20snowboarding%2C%20my%20wrists%20were%20aching%20from%20falling%20forward%20onto%20my%20hands%20all%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20calves%20were%20also%20not%20prepared%20for%20snowboarding.%20While%20on%20a%20snowboard%2C%20you%20use%20the%20toeside%20and%20heelside%20edge%20of%20the%20board%20to%20turn.%20After%20many%20toeside%20turns%2C%20my%20calves%20burned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkiing%20was%20also%20a%20hard%20workout.%20%26quot%3BPizza-ing%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20when%20you%20point%20your%20skis%20into%20a%20triangle%20to%20stop%2C%20can%20strain%20your%20knees.%20That's%20the%20technique%20I%20was%20taught%2C%20and%20by%20the%20end%20of%20my%20first%20day%20on%20skis%2C%20my%20knees%20were%20sore%20from%20all%20the%20%26quot%3Bpizza-ing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20my%20body%20was%20exhausted%20by%20the%20end%20of%20my%20first%20day%20on%20both%20a%20snowboard%20and%20skis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20biggest%20difference%20I%20spotted%20between%20the%20two%20was%20learning%20how%20to%20stop.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222034%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20base%20of%20the%20Winter%20Park%20Resort%20in%20Colorado.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676b0015e3e473ef263b0dd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221526%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20base%20of%20the%20Winter%20Park%20Resort%20in%20Colorado.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20biggest%20concern%20with%20learning%20how%20to%20ski%20and%20snowboard%20was%20learning%20how%20to%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20either%20of%20the%20sports%20safely%20and%20comfortably%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20needed%20to%20be%20confident%20in%20my%20ability%20to%20brake%20quickly%20and%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20this%20skill%20took%20little%20time%20to%20learn%20on%20a%20snowboard.%20With%20my%20board%20perpendicular%20to%20the%20slope%2C%20I%20could%20put%20downward%20pressure%20on%20my%20heels%20and%20immediately%20stop.%20While%20I%20wasn't%20able%20to%20get%20down%20mountains%20on%20my%20first%20snowboarding%20day%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20feel%20comfortable%20stopping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn't%20the%20case%20for%20skiing.%20Anytime%20I%20picked%20up%20any%20speed%2C%20my%20%26quot%3Bpizza-ing%26quot%3B%20maneuver%20wasn't%20strong%20enough%20to%20slow%20me%20down.%20Instead%2C%20I%20spent%20my%20first%20day%20stopping%20by%20intentionally%20falling%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20sure%20it's%20a%20skill%20I%20could%20learn%20on%20skis%2C%20but%20the%20confidence%20I%20had%20with%20stopping%20on%20snowboards%20was%20enough%20to%20stick%20with%20that%20sport%20instead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEveryone%20told%20me%20that%20%26quot%3Bsnowboarding%20is%20harder%20to%20learn%20but%20easier%20to%20master%2C%20while%20skiing%20is%20easier%20to%20learn%20and%20harder%20to%20master.%26quot%3B%20So%20far%2C%20I%20think%20the%20saying%20rings%20true.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222046%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20snowboarding%20at%20the%20Winter%20Park%20Resort.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63c72328eee94d001a78bd29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221535%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20snowboarding%20at%20the%20Winter%20Park%20Resort.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Sproles%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20winters%20in%20Colorado%2C%20I%20imagine%20I've%20heard%20the%20phrase%20close%20to%20a%20hundred%20times%20from%20friends.%20And%20I've%20recited%20it%20nearly%20as%20much%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20after%20trying%20both%2C%20I'm%20starting%20to%20understand%20why%20it's%20said%20so%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20first%20day%20on%20a%20snowboard%20last%20year%20was%20disastrous%2C%20my%20second%20day%20went%20much%20smoother.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20day%20two%2C%20I%20could%20get%20down%20blue%20runs%2C%20and%20after%20about%20five%20days%2C%20I%20felt%20confident%20navigating%20on%20the%20heelside%20and%20toeside%20edges%20of%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20quite%20as%20confident%20yet%20with%20skiing.%20I've%20skied%20only%20one%20day%2C%20and%20although%20I%20fell%20far%20less%20than%20I%20did%20snowboarding%2C%20keeping%20my%20feet%20perfectly%20parallel%20seems%20like%20a%20skill%20that%20would%20take%20months%2C%20if%20not%20years%2C%20to%20master.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20trying%20both%2C%20I%20think%20there's%20nothing%20like%20gliding%20down%20a%20snowy%20mountain%20on%20a%20sunny%20day%20%E2%