sponses%20of%20the%20audit%20firm%20to%20its%20queries%20as%20well%20as%20other%20records%2C%20NFRA%20said%20prima%20facie%20auditors%20had%20not%20discharged%20their%20professional%20duties%20under%20the%20Companies%20Act%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Standards%20on%20Auditing%20(SA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%2030-page%20order%20dated%20December%2023%2C%20NFRA%20said%20auditors%20failed%20to%20meet%20the%20relevant%20requirements%20of%20the%20SAs%20and%20violated%20the%20Act%20in%20respect%20of%20certain%20significant%20related%20party%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20watchdog%20has%20imposed%20a%20monetary%20penalty%20of%20Rs%202%20crore%20on%20Deloitte%20Haskins%20%26amp%3B%20Sells%20LLP%2C%20apart%20from%20penalties%20on%20AB%20Jani%20and%20Rakesh%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20individuals%20have%20been%20debarred%20from%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20appointed%20as%20an%20auditor%20or%20internal%20auditor%20or%20from%20undertaking%20any%20audit%20in%20respect%20of%20financial%20statements%20or%20internal%20audit%20of%20the%20functions%20and%20activities%20of%20any%20company%20or%20body%20corporate%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20varying%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20on%20AB%20Jani%20and%20Rakesh%20Sharma%20is%20for%205%20and%203%20years%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Deloitte%20spokesperson%20said%20it%20has%20received%20the%20NFRA%20order%20against%20the%20firm%20and%20two%20retired%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20currently%20reviewing%20the%20order%20to%20determine%20our%20next%20course%20of%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202018%2C%20the%20ZEEL%20Chairman%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20promoter%20of%20Essel%20Group%20of%20companies%2C%20issued%20a%20letter%20to%20Yes%20Bank%2C%20committing%20Rs%20200%20crore%20fixed%20deposit%20of%20ZEEL%20as%20a%20guarantee%20for%20the%20loans%20given%20by%20Yes%20Bank%20to%20a%20promoter%20group%20company%20Essel%20Green%20Mobility%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20appropriated%20the%20fixed%20deposit%20in%20July%202019%20towards%20the%20settlement%20of%20loan%20amounts%20due%20from%20seven%20promoter%20group%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20the%20creation%20and%20maintenance%20of%20fixed%20deposit%20nor%20its%20reappropriation%20by%20the%20bank%20was%20with%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20board%20or%20shareholders%20of%20the%20company.%20The%20statutory%20auditors%20failed%20to%20identify%20and%20report%20this%20misrepresentation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20regulator%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20NFRA%20said%20its%20examination%20showed%20that%20the%20auditors%20were%20grossly%20negligent%2C%20failed%20to%20apply%20professional%20scepticism%20and%20due%20diligence%2C%20did%20not%20adequately%20challenge%20the%20management's%20assertions%2C%20and%20failed%20to%20evaluate%20the%20reporting%20of%20suspected%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20evident%20from%20unauthorised%20guarantees%2Fsecurities%2C%20premature%20closure%20of%20the%20fixed%20deposit%20by%20the%20bank%20and%20unauthorised%20use%20of%20ZEEL's%20funds%20for%20settling%20the%20loan%20of%20the%20promoter%20group%20companies%2C%20with%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20group%20and%20management%20of%20ZEEL%2C%20the%20regulator%20said%20in%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20show%20cause%20notice%20was%20issued%20to%20the%20audit%20firm%20and%20the%20two%20auditors%2C%20and%20after%20considering%20their%20responses%2C%20the%20watchdog%20found%20that%20the%20audit%20firm%20and%20the%20two%20auditors%20%26quot%3Bare%20guilty%20of%20professional%20misconduct%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20latest%20order%20was%20passed%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%