r%20approach%20unique%20is%20that%20we%20invite%20people%20to%20our%20farm%20and%20allocate%20a%20portion%20of%20land%20where%20we%20grow%20vegetables%20on%20their%20behalf.%20We%20offer%2018%20types%20of%20vegetables%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20season.%20Families%20can%20visit%20for%20regular%20monitoring%20and%20pluck%20the%20produce%20whenever%20they%20want.%20For%20convenience%2C%20we%20also%20deliver%20the%20fresh%20harvest%20to%20their%20homes.%20Our%20setup%20provides%20complete%20traceability%20of%20seasonal%20harvests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMantaj%20shares%20that%20the%20idea%20was%20to%20make%20producing%20organic%20food%20easier%20for%20urban%20families.%20%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20cities%2C%20you%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20source%20of%20your%20food.%20Many%20families%20desire%20to%20eat%20organic%20food%20but%20they%20lack%20sufficient%20land%2C%20time%2C%20and%20expertise%20to%20grow%20it.%20Only%20those%20deeply%20passionate%20about%20gardening%20can%20afford%20to%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fgill-organics-2_11zon-1-1735017685.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gill%20Organics%20supplies%20fresh%20harvests%20to%20families%20in%20Patiala%2C%20Ludhiana%2C%20and%20Chandigarh.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fgill-organics-2_11zon-1-1735017685.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fgill-organics-2_11zon-1-1735017685-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fgill-organics-2_11zon-1-1735017685-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fgill-organics-2_11zon-1-1735017685-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fe